Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.76,0:36:34.08,SK,,0,0,0,,my secret eau de toilette…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.20,0:36:47.30,SK,,0,0,0,,my secret eau de toilette…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.30,0:36:50.64,SK,,0,0,0,,la la love potion　脳下垂体へ届け\Nla la love potion   传送到脑下垂体
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.86,0:36:57.48,SK,,0,0,0,,瞳孔が開くその瞬間を見せて\N让我看看你瞳孔放大的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.42,0:37:00.62,SK,,0,0,0,,my secret eau de toilette
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.62,0:37:04.20,SK,,0,0,0,,じきに君は　falling loveの兆しみせる\N你很快就会有 falling love的征兆出现
